claim.claim-text:
1. A network image processing apparatus comprising: 
an image processor that processes image; 
a network transmission/reception unit that transmits and receives data via a network; 
an inquiry receiver that connects to said network transmission/reception unit at an interval given by an interval setting, and receives inquiries from a plurality of monitoring apparatus inquiring about status information of the network image processing apparatus; 
a response unit that replies to the monitoring apparatus with the status information designated by the inquiry; 
an interval determiner that determines an optimum value of connection interval of the monitoring apparatus according to connection status with the monitoring apparatus; and 
an interval update requester that notifies the monitoring apparatus of the optimum value and requests the monitoring apparatus to update the interval setting with the optimum value.

5. A monitoring apparatus comprising: 
a network transmission/reception unit that transmits/receives data via a network; 
an inquiry unit that connects to a network image processing apparatus at an interval given by a interval setting and inquires about status information of the network image processing apparatus via the network; 
a reply receiver that receives status information from the network image processing apparatus; 
a notification unit that notifies a user of the status information; and 
an interval update unit that receives a notification of the optimum value of the connection interval with the monitoring apparatus, which is determined based on the connecting status, and updates the interval setting with the optimum value.

9. A monitoring method that monitors a network image processing apparatus from a connecting monitoring apparatus via a network, the network image processing apparatus comprising a image processing unit that processes image and a network transmission/reception unit that transmits/receives data via network, the method comprising: 
the monitoring apparatus inquiring about status information by connecting to the network image processing apparatus via the network at an interval given by the interval setting; 
the network image processing apparatus replying with the status information designated by an inquiry, upon receiving an inquiry; 
the monitoring apparatus receiving the reply status information; 
the monitoring apparatus notifying a user of the status information; 
the network image processing apparatus determining an optimum value of connection interval of the monitoring apparatus according to connection status of the network image processing apparatus; 
the network image processing apparatus requesting the monitoring apparatus to update the interval setting with the optimum value, by notifying the monitoring apparatus of the optimum value; and 
the monitoring apparatus updating the interval setting with the optimum value, upon receiving the notification of optimum value of the interval.

10. A network image processing apparatus that includes a function providing status information to a plurality of monitoring apparatuses connected via a network comprising: 
a receiver that receives an inquiry request relating to status information from each monitoring apparatus; 
a response unit that replies to said monitoring apparatus with the status information corresponding to the reception inquiry request; 
an access interval determining unit that determines a plurality of access intervals distributing transmission time for a next inquiry request from the monitoring apparatus, each access interval having different time length and indicating a minimum wait time for the next inquiry request that is transmitted by the monitoring apparatus; 
an access interval informing unit that informs the monitoring apparatus of the determined access interval; 
wherein the monitoring apparatus transmits the next inquiry request when at least the determined access interval elapsed after transmission time for a previous inquiry request.
